commit.message: Fix missing since date for new API
Add missing g_main_context_pop_thread_default which was causing tests to fail in Glib 2.77
Fix leak in theme response processing
Fix leak in mock snapd log handler
Fix read overflow in json-seq parsing
Fix json-seq not working on payloads over multiple reads
Parse json-seq as each seq is received.
Process HTTP chunk as they are received
Use correct json-seq decoding for logs

Fix buffer overflow reading assertions

As discovered using valgrind.
Don't use deprecated function in example
Use .deb version of meson in more recent version of Ubuntu
